[
    {
        "text": "“Hi.",
        "start": 0.16,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m Pete Farrelly, co-writer\nand director of “Green Book.”",
        "start": 0.66,
        "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
        "text": "“Green Book” is the story\nof Don Shirley, a concert",
        "start": 5.46,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "pianist played by Mahershala\nAli, who, in 1962, had",
        "start": 8.52,
        "duration": 4.35
    },
    {
        "text": "to go on a tour of the south.",
        "start": 12.87,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "He hired a bouncer, Tony Lip,\nplayed by Viggo Mortensen",
        "start": 14.43,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "here, to drive him.",
        "start": 18.51,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a scene early on in\nthe movie when they stopped",
        "start": 20.46,
        "duration": 3.17
    },
    {
        "text": "to get a pack of cigarettes.",
        "start": 23.63,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "And Tony Lip gets out, finds\na jade stone on the ground,",
        "start": 25.2,
        "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
        "text": "but it’s next to where\nthey’re selling gemstones.",
        "start": 30.0,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Obviously somebody\ndropped it there.",
        "start": 32.1,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "He puts it in his pocket.",
        "start": 34.02,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Thinks, well, it’s\non the ground.",
        "start": 35.1,
        "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
        "text": "I can have it.",
        "start": 36.475,
        "duration": 0.845
    },
    {
        "text": "And is accused of stealing\nit by the other band members.",
        "start": 37.32,
        "duration": 2.372
    },
    {
        "text": "The point of this scene\nis — it’s a true story,",
        "start": 39.692,
        "duration": 1.958
    },
    {
        "text": "by the way — that it’s\nsomething that Tony Lip told",
        "start": 41.65,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "us —",
        "start": 44.29,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "we had audiotapes of\nTony Lip telling stories",
        "start": 44.79,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "about Dr. Shirley\ntrying to teach him.",
        "start": 47.01,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "He said, you know,\nI love that man —",
        "start": 49.11,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Dr. Shirley — and\nthe reason I do",
        "start": 51.21,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "is because he was always\ntrying to make me smart.”",
        "start": 52.73,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "“Before we pull out, Tony,\nwe need to have a talk.”",
        "start": 58.02,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "“Eh?”",
        "start": 62.9,
        "duration": 0.885
    },
    {
        "text": "“Oleg told me what you did.”",
        "start": 63.785,
        "duration": 1.805
    },
    {
        "text": "“What’d I do?”",
        "start": 65.59,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "“You stole a jade\nstone from the store.”",
        "start": 66.89,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, I didn’t.”",
        "start": 69.24,
        "duration": 0.68
    },
    {
        "text": "“He watched you do it.”",
        "start": 69.92,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "“I didn’t steal no stone.”",
        "start": 71.3,
        "duration": 1.936
    },
    {
        "text": "“You picked it up and\nput it in your pocket.”",
        "start": 73.236,
        "duration": 1.874
    },
    {
        "text": "“I picked up a rock\noff o' the ground.",
        "start": 75.11,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "I didn’t steal from a box.”",
        "start": 76.75,
        "duration": 1.302
    },
    {
        "text": "“Now, why would you pick\nup a rock off the ground?”",
        "start": 78.052,
        "duration": 2.143
    },
    {
        "text": "“I don’t know.",
        "start": 80.195,
        "duration": 2.405
    },
    {
        "text": "Because it ain’t stealing.",
        "start": 82.6,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s just a regular rock.”",
        "start": 84.13,
        "duration": 1.335
    },
    {
        "text": "“And why would you\nwant a regular rock?”",
        "start": 85.465,
        "duration": 2.655
    },
    {
        "text": "“To have.",
        "start": 88.12,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "For luck, maybe.”",
        "start": 89.22,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "“A lucky rock?”",
        "start": 90.34,
        "duration": 1.255
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yeah.”",
        "start": 91.595,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“Let me see it.”",
        "start": 92.095,
        "duration": 1.517
    },
    {
        "text": "“The thing that really\ncomes through here",
        "start": 93.612,
        "duration": 1.708
    },
    {
        "text": "is a parent-child\nrelationship is forming.",
        "start": 95.32,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Dr. Shirley is educated.",
        "start": 98.56,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Tony Lip’s — sixth\ngrade education,",
        "start": 101.53,
        "duration": 1.926
    },
    {
        "text": "but really didn’t pay\nattention after third grade.”",
        "start": 103.456,
        "duration": 2.124
    },
    {
        "text": "“Take it back and pay for it.”",
        "start": 108.12,
        "duration": 2.065
    },
    {
        "text": "“And he’s being\nschooled by Dr. Shirley.",
        "start": 110.185,
        "duration": 2.759
    },
    {
        "text": "Dr. Shirley — if he’s gonna\nbe spending a couple of months",
        "start": 112.944,
        "duration": 2.416
    },
    {
        "text": "with him, he’s\ntrying to help him",
        "start": 115.36,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "in the way he talks, the way\nhe speaks, the way he treats",
        "start": 117.04,
        "duration": 2.375
    },
    {
        "text": "people, the way he acts.”",
        "start": 119.415,
        "duration": 4.42
    },
    {
        "text": "“Do not drive,\nMr. Vallelonga.”",
        "start": 123.835,
        "duration": 1.995
    },
    {
        "text": "“It helps that Dr.\nShirley’s in control",
        "start": 125.83,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "when he doesn’t get out.",
        "start": 127.72,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "He doesn’t do anything.",
        "start": 128.77,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "He sits there.",
        "start": 129.82,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "And Tony has to turn\nto him, and Tony",
        "start": 131.05,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "has to stretch\naround him, and he’s",
        "start": 132.73,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "just such a child in\nthis scene, the way he",
        "start": 134.59,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "reacts to everything.",
        "start": 136.57,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s like if you caught\na five-year-old stealing",
        "start": 137.77,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "gum at the grocery store.",
        "start": 140.23,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s how he reacts.",
        "start": 142.18,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "I liked Viggo having\nto turn toward him,",
        "start": 145.27,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "and it just felt like\nhe was at a disadvantage",
        "start": 148.03,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "in that scene.",
        "start": 151.06,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "And it helped\nempower Dr. Shirley",
        "start": 152.11,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "that he could just sit\nback and control it.”",
        "start": 154.21,
        "duration": 3.97
    },
    {
        "text": "“If you’d like, Tony, I’d\nhappily buy you the stone.”",
        "start": 158.18,
        "duration": 2.425
    },
    {
        "text": "“Don’t bother.",
        "start": 160.605,
        "duration": 0.995
    },
    {
        "text": "You took all the\nfun out of it.”",
        "start": 161.6,
        "duration": 2.92
    }
]